## PyCharm

1. To add " \" (space + newline) as the end of a line. We can do `search and replace` using Regex. Search for "$" and replace for `\ \\`. 


## Hydra
1. When running python script which has hydra, in shell script, if there is equal sign, you have to escape it using `\=`. If you submit a yaml file job, you have to use four slash signs `\\\\=`

## Exposure Bias
During training, context is from ground truth. At inference time, the context is generated by model itself. This kind of mismatch is called exposure bias. 



## Relu and SwiGlu
For relu, we have to use higher learning rate and for swiGlu smaller init for gating params